職能治療技術學實習                      


  	This course contains 1 lecturer and 2 practice credits. Practice is emphasized to facilitate experiential learning about professional issues. It reviews some professional basics and introduces some advanced practice guidelines to prepare the occupational therapy students for fieldwork practice. Through the semester, the crafts, modalidities, and techniques are introduced with practice experience. The issues of therapentic relationship, clinical reasoning, activity analysis and application are addressed to build up the professional identity. Evidence-based practice are emphasized through hand-on experience of scientific literature review and in-class discussion

課程教育目標 

A. 培育具有專業知能的職能治療人才B. 培育具有人本關懷的職能治療人才C. 培育具有主動求知、終身學習及貢獻科學研究之發展的職能治療人才 
課程基本素養與核心能力 

[核心能力]職能治療專業知識與理論
具備職能治療專業知識理論基礎，以為專業技能奠基。職能治療專業技能
具備職能治療專業技能，以提供個案職能表現之評估、分析與治療的能力。溝通表達及團隊合作之能力
培養適切溝通表達及團隊合作能力，以建立良好的醫病關係及專業團隊互動。獨立思考及問題解決之能力
培養具有獨立思考、臨床推理及問題解決的能力，並能終身學習。 
