參考書目 References
	    1. Case-Smith, J., Allen, A. S., & Pratt, P. N. (2010). Occupational therapy for children (6th ed.). Toronto: Mosby.
2. Davies, P. M. (2000). Steps to follow: The comprehensive treatment of patients with hemiplegia. New York: Springer-Verlag.
3. Pendleton, H. M. & Schultz-Krohn, W. (2012). Pedretti’s Occupational therapy: Practice skills for physical dysfunction (7th ed.). St. Louis, MO: Mosby/Elsevier.
4. Radomski, M. V., & Trombly Latham, C. A. (2013). Occupational therapy for physical dysfunction (7th ed.). Baltimore, MD: Lippincott Williams & Wilkins.
5. Schell, B. A. B., Gillen, G., Scaffa, M., & Cohn, E. S. (2013). Willard and Spackman's occupational therapy (12th ed.). New York: Mosby.
6. Zoltan, B. (2007). Vision, perception and cognition: A manual for the evaluation and treatment of the neurologically impaired adult (4th ed.). Thorofare, NJ: Slack.    

